snippet.title: Gimmick! 2 - Accolades Trailer - Nintendo Switch | Steam | PS4 | PS5 | Xbox
snippet.description:
Wishlist on PlayStation: https://store.playstation.com/en-se/concept/10011826
Wishlist on Xbox: https://www.microsoft.com/store/productid/9nfkg9ksg2hs
Buy on Nintendo eShop: https://www.nintendo.com/us/store/products/gimmick-2-switch/
Buy on Steam: http://s.team/a/2994880/ 

Embark on a sparkling journey in this long-awaited sequel to SUNSOFT’s legendary NES™ platformer Gimmick! Solve puzzles, trick enemies, and explore a physics-based playground.

PlayStation 4, PlayStation 5, Xbox One, and Xbox Series S|X versions will launch on January 30!

Follow Clear River Games on X for updates: http://www.x.com/clearrivergames
